These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, balloon-flower, amaryllis
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, australian, american
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, june, july
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, mauve, orange
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding, tennis
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, van
 1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
 2. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
 3. the australian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 6. the australian is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the dutch is the person who growsiris##1
 8. the person driving the boat is the person who likes mauve##1
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who likes mauve and the person driving the van##2
10. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
11. the dutch is the person who likes orange##1
12. the american is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |
| Flower          | iris   | amaryllis            | balloon-flower     |
| Nationality           | dutch | american | australian |
| Birthday   | march      | july               | june        |
| Color           | orange        | black         | mauve   |
| Sport         | tennis     | skateboarding      | golf       |
| Transport     | van        | train              | boat       |

