.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, milk
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, july, march
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bolivar, davidoff
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, r&b, trance
House: gothic-revival, wooden, colonial
City: colone, rome, marseilles
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is the davidoff-smoker##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 3. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is the fan of ambient##1
 5. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person who's birthday is in december and the aristoff-smoker##2
 6. the gothic-revival house is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person traveling to colone##2
 7. the person drinking milk is the wooden house##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3
10. the fan of trance is the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | lemonade | milk        |
| Birthday          | july   | march    | december        |
| Cigar   | aristoff    | bolivar | davidoff |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | ambient  | r&b         |
| House           | colonial    | gothic-revival | wooden       |
| City     | rome   | marseilles    | colone  |

