.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, mauve, orange
There 3 different types of food: apricot, eggplant, raspberry
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, quad-bike, motorbike
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, entrepreneur, scientist
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, techno, blues
House: farmhouse, ranch-style, futuristic
 1. the chef is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
 2. the scientist is the person eating raspberry##1
 3. the fan of techno is the person who likes mauve##1
 4. the farmhouse house is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person eating apricot is between the person driving the quad-bike and the ranch-style house##2
 6. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
 7. the person who likes mauve is in an odd position##4
 8. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 9. the scientist is on the far right##1
10. the person driving the motorbike is in an odd position##4
11. the person driving the quad-bike is the entrepreneur##1
12. the fan of techno is on the far left##1
13. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3       |
| Color      | mauve        | turquise     | orange          |
| Food          | eggplant     | apricot | raspberry    |
| Transport         | quad-bike    | snowmobile  | motorbike |
| Job           | entrepreneur | chef    | scientist    |
| Music-Genre   | techno      | blues | country      |
| House           | farmhouse          | futuristic     | ranch-style         |

