.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, sprite
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, apricot, amber
3 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, mah-jongg
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, gospel, soul
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, corn, tomato
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, may, june
 1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 3. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 4. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 5. the fan of d&b is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who likes amber##2
 6. the person eating corn is on the far right##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 8. the person playing monopoly is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 9. the person eating cauliflower is in an odd position##4
10. the person eating tomato is in an even position##4
11. the person eating corn is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person who likes amber is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | sprite      | fanta        |
| Color         | amber   | blue     | apricot |
| Game   | monopoly | mah-jongg | backgammon     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | d&b         | soul         |
| Food   | cauliflower   | tomato     | corn      |
| Birthday         | february  | june     | may         |

