.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, fishing, photography
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, april, february
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, coral, ivory
3 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, poker
There 3 different types of food: garlic, lettuce, cranberry
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, tennis
 1. the person who likes azure is in an even position##4
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is the person playing poker##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
 5. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 9. the person eating cranberry is between the person who likes coral and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
10. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |
| Hobby         | cooking      | fishing   | photography |
| Birthday           | february | september | april      |
| Color   | ivory | azure     | coral     |
