.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-6::.
House: victorian, art-deco, ranch-style
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, family, time-travel
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, lemonade
There 3 different types of food: lime, pineapple, spinach
3 different pets are kept: lizard, rat, snake
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, cycling, weightlifting
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is cycling##2
 2. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person drinking coffee##1
 4. the owner of the rat is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person eating spinach is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 6. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person eating lime##1
10. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
11. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |
| House           | victorian | art-deco | ranch-style |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | family     | time-travel    |
| Beverage   | lemonade       | soy-milk | coffee        |
| Food   | spinach       | lime   | pineapple        |
| Pet           | rat        | lizard     | snake          |
| Sport     | cycling  | weightlifting    | soccer       |

