 3. the person eating zucchini is the person traveling to london##1
 4. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
 6. the alhambra-smoker is the person playing whist##1
 7. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
 8. the person watching disaster movies is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
10. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |
