 6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
 7. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 8. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
11. the architect is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
