.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, romance, spy
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, bike
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, pink, yellow
There are 3 different nationalities: british, german, nigerian
City: marseilles, miami, berlin
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the nigerian##1
2. the person who likes pink is between the person watching romance movies and the nigerian##2
3. the british is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
5. the person traveling to miami is on the far left##1
6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the person who likes grey is the person watching spy movies##1
8. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person drinking juice##2
9. the person watching romance movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |         2          |      3      |
| Beverage      | juice    | iced-tea           | 7up         |
| Movie-Genre         | spy   | horror             | romance  |
| Transport           | bike  | ship | quad-bike |
| Color   | grey      | pink              | yellow      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | german             | british     |
| City         | miami   | marseilles           | berlin      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-19::.
City: paris, miami, colone
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, balloon-flower, orchid
3 different games are played: scrabble, domino, bridge
3 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse, snake
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, sailing
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, lemonade
 1. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
 2. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
 8. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person traveling to miami##1
10. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |
| City          | miami    | colone  | paris   |
| Flower   | balloon-flower      | daisy  | orchid  |
| Game   | scrabble | domino  | bridge |
| Pet           | mouse     | lizard   | snake   |
| Sport         | baseball  | climbing | sailing |
| Beverage     | lemonade   | 7up      | almond-milk  |

