.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-20::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, lily, poppy
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, gardening, woodworking
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, mechanic, photographer
3 different games are played: domino, snooker, canasta
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, havana, vegafina
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, helicopter, train
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person driving the train##1
 2. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 3. the person playing canasta is the person who growsbellflower##1
 4. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the photographer is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
 8. the librarian is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3
 9. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the mechanic##1
10. the mechanic is the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |
| Flower          | lily     | poppy   | bellflower     |
| Hobby         | woodworking | collecting   | gardening  |
| Job           | librarian   | photographer | mechanic   |
| Game   | domino    | snooker       | canasta    |
| Cigar   | vegafina        | siglo    | havana   |
| Transport         | helicopter      | taxi     | train |

 